air:Brand.Name: Business flex
air:Brand.air:Title: Business flex
Biz flex
air:Brand.air:Text:
A total flexible ticket to go with what is simply an outstanding flight experience with the brand new Austrian Business Class seat featuring:
- a horizontal full-flat bed almost 2 metres in length - an innovative air cushion system providing greatest possible comfort - an integrated massage function - the latest on board entertainment system with over 100 hours of entertainment on demand
All this coupled with gourmet delights served by our catering company DOCO.

air:Brand.Name: Premium Economy Flex
air:Brand.air:Title: Premium Economy Flex
PremEcoFlx
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Premium Economy for up to 50% more legroom

A new travel experience between Business Class and Economy Class. More space, more service and more extras
Full flexibility to change or cancel your reservation free of charge, plus:
· Up to 50% more legroom and personal space · Check in 2 bags, each weighing up to 23 kg · Welcome drink on board · In flight entertainment on an 11- or 12-inch monitor operated by remote control · A greater selection of meals, served on china tableware · Accessories bag by your seat · Airport lounge access available for an additional fee
If the flight will be operated by another airline, then there maybe differences in the onboard product or service.
Premium Economy - look forward to a new travel experience

air:Brand.Name: Economy flexible
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy flexible
Eco flex
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Economy flexible for the option to amend or cancel your reservation free of charge when required

Austrian Airlines Economy flexible tickets offer the highest level of flexibility and convience. Ideal for our clients travelling for work.
In 2013 the entire longhaul fleet was redesigned with a completely new cabin interior.
New ergonomic Economy Class seats featuring a unique relax position make your flight even more comfortable.
Enjoy entertainment from a 9in touch screen and special meals created by our catering partner DOCO.
Full flexibility for our busiest passengers
